      "text": [
        "4706 - وَ قَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"بِرُّ اَلرَّجُلِ بِوَلَدِهِ بِرُّهُ بِوَالِدَيْهِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4706 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"A man's kindness to his child is a form of his kindness to his own parents.\""
        ]
      }
    }
